      • addBid

        public void addBid(Bid bid)
            throws NullIDException
        Add the Bid to the user. This verifies that the bid is not already in the user, and that the bid is made by this user. The bids are transient; the only thing stored consistently is a list of the IDs of the bids. This means that the bids should be have an ID before adding this item to the user.
        Parameters:
        bid -
        Throws:
        NullIDException - The bid has no ID.
